<span id="freeTextContainer10645907677887397483">4.75⭐️<br/><br/>This series is too fucking fantastic. I can’t... this is just too much! <br/><br/>I rarely RARELY ever read a book where I don’t come out the other end complaining about one thing or another. However much I love the book there’s always something that I’m let down by. <br/>This is, by no means, the case here. By far, it is not! <br/><br/>Where do I begin? And why am I not giving this 5 starts? <br/>I loved everything! The plot. The world. The political intricacies. My adorable, incredible characters. EVERYTHING! <br/><br/></span>

